  <description>
    <p>Pulsar is a desktop app for downloading media, converting formats, and compressing files.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download video and audio with advanced options.</li>
      <li>Convert media and files between multiple formats.</li>
      <li>Compress output with quality and size controls.</li>
      <li>Manage multiple jobs in a shared processing queue.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
